/on_status response can be solicited or unsolicited;
/on_status returns theaudit trail for order items(including status of item returns, cancels processed or in-progress), the current state of order items & fulfillments, order quote & breakup;
Buyer app can send NACK for /on_status with error code for cases such as:
NACK received by seller app for /on_confirm but seller app sends /on_status to update order state to "Accepted";
In case of NACK received for /on_status, seller app should rollback order to previous state of the order, i.e.thestate prior to sending /on_status;
